  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 7th level, your hive accumulates around your body in attempt to regulate your temperature. You gain advantage on all checks or saving throws as a result of a cold or warm environment.</p><p>Additionally, whenever you would be attempting to make an Intimidation (Charisma) check against a creature you may instead use your Animal Handling (Wisdom) as your hive aggressively buzzes.</p><p>At 11th level, when a creature would fail an Intimidation check as a result of your <em><strong>Bearding</strong></em> clan feature they gain 1 rank of <strong>Demoralized</strong>.</p>",
